      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The software implementation of our approach is named mummichog",
      "asbval:note": "Paper describes Mummichog (version 1, 2013), not Mummichog 3. Paper does not mention GitHub organization, metabolomics-cloud, or repository migration. The card describes a software engineering/DevOps task (repository migration, packaging, CI/CD conformance) that is entirely absent from the paper. The paper only documents the original algorithm and its application.",
