      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "From the m/z features in [significant list], mummichog computes all possibly matched metabolites, and searches the reference metabolic network for all the modules that can be formed by these tentative metabolites... The m/z - metabolite matching considers all common isotopic derivatives and adducts.",
