      "asbval:note": "The paper (Li et al. 2013) describes mummichog as a computational method for metabolomics analysis published in PLOS Computational Biology. It does not discuss package migration, relocation, GitHub organization changes, CI/CD workflows, or installation verification procedures. The paper is a scientific methods paper, not a software engineering/DevOps task card.",
