    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/untargeted-metabolomics-feature-analysis/004",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "From user input, mummichog requires two lists of m/z features, the significant list (e.g. selected by univariate statistics) and the reference list (all features detected in the MS experiment)... mummichog computes all possibly matched metabolites, and searches the reference metabolic network for all the modules that can be formed by these tentative metabolites",
